## Quick Start

{{CONDITIONAL:mode-astro}}
Import in your global CSS or BaseLayout:
```css
@import '../styles/design-system/index.css';
```
Start the dev server: `pnpm dev` → `http://localhost:4321/design-system`
{{/CONDITIONAL}}

{{CONDITIONAL:mode-standalone}}
Link the CSS in your HTML:
```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="./assets/css/index.css">
<script src="./assets/js/design-system.js" defer></script>
```
Serve: `python3 -m http.server 8080` → `http://localhost:8080/design-system.html`
{{/CONDITIONAL}}

